Package: ggsignif
Type: Package
Title: Easily add significance bars to your ggplots
Version: 0.1.0
Author@R: person("Constantin", "Ahlmann-Eltze", email = "artjom31415@googlemail.com")
Description: This package provides an easy way to indicate if two groups are significantly different.
  Commonly this is shown with a by a bar on top connecting the groups of interest which itself is annoted with the level of significance (NS, *, **, ***).
  The package provides a single layer (geom_signif) that takes the groups for comparison and the test (t.test, wilcox etc.) and adds the annotation
  to the plot.
URL: https://github.com/Artjom-Metro/ggsignif
License: GNU GPLv3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  ggplot2   (>= 2.0.0)
